Below is a simple HTML template for a one-page website offering UX/UI design services for cryptocurrency projects. This includes sections for an introduction, services, about the company, portfolio, and contact form.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Crypto UX/UI Design Services</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
            background: #f4f4f4;
        }
        header, footer {
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        nav {
            background: #444;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
        }
        .services, .about, .portfolio, .contact {
            padding: 20px 0;
